description:
ManageSellOfferOp is an XDR Struct defines as:

```text struct ManageSellOfferOp { Asset selling; Asset buying; int64 amount; // amount being sold. if set to 0, delete the offer Price price;  // price of thing being sold in terms of what you are buying

// 0=create a new offer, otherwise edit an existing offer int64 offerID; }; ```

Asset.description:
Asset is an XDR Union defines as:

```text union Asset switch (AssetType type) { case ASSET_TYPE_NATIVE: // Not credit void;

case ASSET_TYPE_CREDIT_ALPHANUM4: AlphaNum4 alphaNum4;

case ASSET_TYPE_CREDIT_ALPHANUM12: AlphaNum12 alphaNum12;

// add other asset types here in the future }; ```
